# The served SPA (apps/hypervisor/product-ui/) + the IOI /api adapter + serve
# (apps/hypervisor/scripts/{serve-live-reference,ioi-api-adapter,ioi-projection,
# ioi-augmentation,ioi-agent-runs,ioi-run-timeline}) are the one runtime. The borrowed
# upstream brand was rebranded gitpod/ona -> ioi, so they are source-neutral and TRACKED.
